# NIVARA AREIS — Dashboard URL (reference only)

The desktop shortcut must NOT point here directly.

## Permanent shortcut (Windows)
1. Double-click **Install-NIVARA-Desktop-Shortcut.bat** in the repo root.
2. Shortcut on Desktop opens `%LOCALAPPDATA%\NIVARA\NIVARA-Dashboard.bat`.
3. URL is stored in `%LOCALAPPDATA%\NIVARA\dashboard.url`.

## If access error appears
1. Double-click **Fix-NIVARA-Shortcut.bat**
2. Click **Deploy** in the wizard → deploy on Streamlit Cloud
3. Set subdomain **nivara-areis** → URL becomes https://nivara-areis.streamlit.app/
4. Paste URL → **Save & Open**

## Deploy settings (copy exactly)
| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Repository | `narendhrareddi-ship-it/Nivara-AREIS` |
| Branch | `main` |
| Main file | `streamlit_app.py` |
| Custom subdomain | `nivara-areis` |

One-click GitHub link:
https://github.com/narendhrareddi-ship-it/Nivara-AREIS/blob/main/streamlit_app.py

## Default target URL (after deploy)
https://nivara-areis.streamlit.app/
